Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:50.04,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}你那无暇的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.46,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}化作照亮明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.67,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}其实早已一直察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:00.51,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}通过双手紧紧拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.80,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}冲口而出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.68,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}流露而出的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.22,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}现在 悄悄 定是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.35,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}蕴含着内心的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.85,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}回转不息的梦境之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.15,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}与你一度一度反复起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:21.53,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}摇曳的景色 旅途在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:25.74,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}伴随着迎面而来的微风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:29.12,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}屡次越过境界线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.29,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}划开云彩 伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:37.75,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}眼泪如今 留于蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.96,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}踏出前进的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:47.97,eromanga edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,100)\blur1}去收获一同觅得的辉煌光彩
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,-----------------ED-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:05.22,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这全都是你亲手做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:07.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 从采购到成品都是我一手包办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是让我见识一下你工作的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如你所见 我这是绝赞工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然而你是小说家来着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那么多 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我将其命名为「春妖精的全裸汤」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:27.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.97,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:13.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是职业作家 这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:14.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:18.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为喜欢的人亲手下厨的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我充分理解女主角为别人做料理的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.08,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我是把写小说当作游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:31.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不认真玩的话岂不是太无聊了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是游戏才要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福 我可能更喜欢下厨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:52.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 这是邻居让我带给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居亲手做的料理 很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:04.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.94,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz13.96\pos(656,800)\c&H7E7277&}邻居？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,eromanga 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.96\pos(772,836)\c&H7E7277&}关系一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:11.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:13.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真色情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢 还有其他要说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:25.37,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么你只会画贫乳的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我要求你把女主角的胸部画大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.39,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会无视掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.26,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我对色色的画有自己的讲究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想画那些自己没有亲眼见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.33,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,亲…亲眼是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那张插画难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太下流了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:03:59.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 好色 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚绝对想象了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,用我来想象十分色情的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定觉得我是为了画出那么色情的插画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.86,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才买那种细绳内裤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后觉得我很色情对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没那么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有想到那种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会用妹妹来想色情的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:26.97,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你多么色情 都不会对你有色欲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况 绝对不会瞧不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像笨蛋似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这种即好色又说谎的哥哥我才不认识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.26,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个莫非是妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.24,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁的山田小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.65,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H7B6B71&\frz33.3\pos(798,894)}邻居？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.65,eromanga 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H7B6B71&\pos(904,904)\frz27.53}关系一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居？关系一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.15,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz36\pos(1658.666,402.667)\c&H7D767D&}呀吼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.11,eromanga 2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz26.43\c&H6A5D63&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\pos(594,422)}邻居亲手做的料理非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,邻居亲手做的料理非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.40,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:13.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我最近经常去隔壁 但那是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:13.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,总是这样 不管什么都谎话连篇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什么的 最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看到你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:33.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要证明我不是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一年里面一直都在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能让你认可我是你真正的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事情我现在清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要让妹妹当女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要写以妹妹为题材的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要写自己最喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后创作出究极的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不开心 不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做才不会让我打开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让我感到恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.73,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,满嘴谎言的哥哥我最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:34.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 干劲全开地做我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼间就也快半个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:54.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后我就再也没有跟纱雾见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:07:00.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 新作的企划请无论如何也要在这个星期交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.36,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍微给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚了 那么请你慢慢思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝工作是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不出新作的话 我的一席之地就会马上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会被粉丝忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么写都出版不了一本书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话一下子就会回到满受挫折的前年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要和这样的恐惧进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我写出了有趣的东西 也很有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,门是开着的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.29,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精老师 不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那我擅自进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.03,eromanga 6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,508)\fs60\c&H735961&\b1}月境办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,妖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 话说今天是约定的日子来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,请在客厅等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看见她那么认真的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.21,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的新作小说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天不是一个字都还没写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力「完成原稿召唤」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1081.6,1004.8)}Summon Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,把完成原稿从魔界召唤出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么可能 居然有这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样能吓得到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在超拼命地赶稿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我从魔界召唤出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是觉得我说谎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就调查一下我的笔记本电脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你删掉了吗 就为了这种无聊的小戏法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山…山田妖精的新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:00.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:05.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看 原稿不就在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负吧 和泉征宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就用我的「神眼」看穿你的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(900.8,1003.2)}God Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意 山田妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:16.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来读一读你这从魔界召唤出来的全力以赴的小说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手和心越读越停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是动画化作家的实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.37,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这部作品 女主角全都是贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是埃罗芒阿老师擅长的姿势 喜欢的场景和服装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 总而言之就是很色情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.56,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全特化到了极限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是为埃罗芒阿老师量身定做的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你这份…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你这份原稿 是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是还是不是啊 征宗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点很重要 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.45,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是很认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 根本赢不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我的原稿有这么有趣吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.45,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 我才没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你居然敢给我看这种东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的 这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:48.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我写的作品肯定比你的好卖百亿倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.53,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不就不能好好一决胜负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.46,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:01.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这份原稿根本不是为了让很多读者开心而写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:08.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你往这里边注入了灵魂 只为了某个人而写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,读完这份不能作为商品的垃圾原稿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.70,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感情会被动摇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:19.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上就只有我和你的妹妹 埃罗芒阿老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,读完以后当然会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.41,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:31.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这就像是写着「埃罗芒阿老师是你的妹妹」一样明显
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:36.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想让我的妹妹读一读这份作品的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:38.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.91,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法肯定会好好传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:46.77,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这份足足有三百页的超超超热烈情书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还以为你的暴露癖是有多严重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:56.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你却居然毫无自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 输了输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你…这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:06.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:10.08,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么色情且有趣的杰作被永远地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是感谢你的夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算留下来也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有她画的插画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:18.93,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有言在先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是我输了 而不是你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.82,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来原稿你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会说出「不打算让妹妹看了」这种话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:42.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给就给 我原本就这么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.73,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是掉下去可就不仅仅是受伤那么简单…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.25,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,埃罗芒阿老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:28.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是…那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 新作的原稿写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:32.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你读读看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 虽然你的做法很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.19,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做那么危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:48.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为从那以后你一直都闭门不开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.59,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.43,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一段时间闭门不开的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗场面 画得好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.55,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,与之前相比简直天差地别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.74,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看了格斗技的比赛视频
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也看了很多武器的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才画得这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:16.83,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我并不太喜欢死人或者受伤的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:22.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我就说过了 不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我对喜欢的角色逝去感到很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至今为止都有所抵触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:32.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是第一次和你面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.12,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,交谈创作的话题的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:38.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我便觉得只把自己喜欢的东西画得好是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我说你画很烂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.34,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我觉得也必须战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.62,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗？是跟我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 也看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.51,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,上色之后就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的是不同发型的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.02,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 连巨乳角色都能驾驭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.16,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是画出能让人看的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.99,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉之后就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,超色情 超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 这半个月她都在练习这些东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老师 这样就清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我负责你的新作是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？ 那是什么 谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:33.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你有事情瞒着我 还和隔壁的山田小姐悄悄碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来还很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥不会在工作以外的地方认识那种女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.35,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,自从你遇见她以后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你就变得十分有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:49.46,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人肯定是新的插画师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就一直关起房门来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:53.96,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:16:00.17,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老师让妹妹成为主角 然后创作出究极的轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.18,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实是非常开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.83,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想着肯定得让我来画插画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.88,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对绝对不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.27,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会把和泉老师让给那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.49,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话该由我说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.61,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁的山田小姐是人气作家山田妖精老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.87,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,山田妖精老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:32.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对 那家伙…那家伙是埃罗芒阿老师的大粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她想和你一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.75,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我赌上了埃罗芒阿老师 跟她进行了小说对决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊 我听都没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.40,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:50.06,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你可能会说「与其和我一起 更想和人气作家一起工作」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.63,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 哥哥真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,连我自己也是这么觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:01.20,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为最后还是得不得不说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.54,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的 那个方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.77,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 但是我已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 居然赢了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和泉老师好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然原本是想让你读完再做决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.42,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初就是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:31.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始也请多指教了 和泉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.98,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是呢 请多指教 埃罗芒阿老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不认识叫那种名字的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.14,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.07,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在慌什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.66,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 才没有慌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有 一点都没有慌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.10,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就过去对面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.64,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:29.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 紧张得快要休克死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.68,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.09,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:40.58,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 我觉得十分有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:41.38,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:46.76,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 就这样出书是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:51.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让别人看 太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:54.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:19:02.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:09.15,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.11,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:15.23,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是兄妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定要当她的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.18,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 这样啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 笑成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:02.44,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 活该
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.50,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 接下来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.47,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.04,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 纱雾 我也有梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:12.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.71,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 非常大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:19.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让这份原稿出书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不能就这样直接出书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.63,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我重新进行构思 写出企划书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.79,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让责编认可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.69,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然要从这一步开始 但是肯定会出成书的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:35.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让很多的人感到有趣并且喜欢上男女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.32,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后人气不断攀升
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:39.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,并且赚得可以轻松生活的费用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.03,eromanga 3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\b1\fs40\c&H6570DF&\frz29.49\pos(273.6,176)}祝贺动画化!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.03,eromanga 3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HE0B12D&\frz30\fs40\pos(345.6,292.8)}和泉先生的签名会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:41.60,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再接着就是动画化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.48,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是哥哥的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对 那些都是准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.01,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是给我们的客厅买上一个大的液晶电视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.13,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再准备一个超贵的音响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.85,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在豪华的蛋糕上面点上蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,把你从房间里面带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:58.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起看动画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:01.92,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,由我负责原作 你负责插画的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:03.28,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:07.31,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我觉得肯定会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.72,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤的事情可能会被一扫而空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:12.86,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.84,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我绝对要实现的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:22.39,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喊得声音太大有点喘不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:26.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 这次也是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:28.05,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.95,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雾 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:46.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你从以前就是这样呢 和泉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:51.80,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,总是都能给予我梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.29,0:22:55.67,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 和泉老师 来大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:59.57,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有趣的事情怎么可以让你独占呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.00,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那不仅仅是你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.65,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,让它成为我们一起的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.30,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.03,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:16.52,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:21.90,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,向着梦想踏出的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.97,0:23:27.78,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概一生都不会忘记这天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.81,eromanga cn,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 和妹妹一起制定轻小说企划
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,eromanga 5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs80\fn@萝莉体 第二版\pos(1726,332)}哥哥...
